data.description: This exquisite 4-bedroom, 2-bathroom home is nestled in a highly sought-after subdivision, offering both convenience and luxury. Step inside to discover high-end finishes throughout. The spacious living area is perfect for entertaining, complemented by a cozy fireplace that creates a warm and inviting atmosphere. The gourmet kitchen is a chef's dream, boasting premium appliances, sleek countertops, and ample storage space. The master suite features a tiled shower and a spacious walk-in closet. Outside has a beautifully landscaped yard equipped with underground sprinklers and a 3-car garage. Additionally, the solar panel loan will be paid off, and gas is only $38 a month, while electricity is $0 a month. A passive radon system is already installed, and a privacy fence will be added in the next 3-4 weeks. Enjoy the bonus room above the garage, adding even more value to this remarkable property.
